}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "1813V1.2" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''Alcor Micro''' Hub IC packages are labeled with the '''ALCOR''' logo, "AU6254", "M41-JBL-GR", "H32817-0", and "0833T".
I don't know what '''Inland''' model this thing is supposed to be. The tagline text above is what is on the top of the (metal) hub casing.
This hub presents itself to the host system as two 058f:6254 devices.
